CHROMA ATE INC (2360)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 43.79% to NT$327,139,000 from NT$581,963,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            327,139          581,963    
YOY%             -43.79%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,202,252        2,046,650   
YOY%             -41.26% 
=================================================================
 